---
import ThemeToggle from "../components/Themetoggle";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { AnimateFragments } from "../components/Hero";
import Jobs from "../components/Jobs";
import Technologies from "../components/Technologies";
import { AwsIcon, GoogleIcon, GitHubIcon, Postman, Notion} from '../icons/Icons'
import TechFront from '../sections/TechFront'
import TechColaborate from '../sections/TechColaborate'
import TechCloud from '../sections/TechCloud'
import { Spotlight } from "../components/ui/Spotlight";

---

<Layout>

  <main
    class="bg-white min-h-screen text-black dark:bg-[#161616] dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300 pb-32"
  >
    <section
      class="fixed left-0 top-0 w-full bg-[#eff3f4] dark:bg-[#1c1c1c] py-3 z-50"
    >
      <div class="mx-6 flex gap-3 items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex gap-3 items-center">
          <img src="/author.png" class="w-12 object-top" alt="" />
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-0">
            <p class="font-semibold text-sm dark:text-secondary">
              Mich Rodriguez
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-terteary ">Frontend React</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ThemeToggle client:load />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pt-28">
      <div class="mx-6 flex flex-col gap-4 relative z-30">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl text-balance text-gray-800 font-semibold min-h-fit dark:text-secondary"
        >
          Soy Desarrollador
          <AnimateFragments
            client:load
            value={'<span class="font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-500 to-gray-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent dark:from-gray-300 dark:to-gray-700">frontend React.</span>'}
          />
        </h1>
        <div
          class="sm:aspect-auto text-gray-800 min-h-min text-pretty dark:text-terteary"
        >
          <AnimateFragments
            client:load
            value={'Hola, <a href="/yo" class="text-[#313438d4] font-extrabold dark:text-secondary dark:font-semibold flex items-center gap-2"><img src="/author_home.png" class="w-7 inline" alt="" /> Soy Mich. </a>Desarrollo experiencias únicas, combinando rendimiento y precisión a través de <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white"><div class="px-3 py-0 rounded-xl bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center"><span class="inline-flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" color="currentColor" fill="none"><path d="M20.0001 11.9998L4.00012 11.9998" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" /><path d="M15.0003 17C15.0003 17 20.0002 13.3176 20.0002 12C20.0002 10.6824 15.0002 7 15.0002 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" /></svg></span></div><p class="text-[#313438d4] font-extrabold dark:text-secondary dark:font-semibold">productos funcionales.</p></a>'}
          />
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-3 text-center mt-0 flex-wrap">
          <a
            href=""
            class="border-2 rounded-lg bg-[#eff3f4] border-[#eff3f4] dark:bg-[#2c2c2c] dark:border-[#2c2c2c] text-xs py-2 px-1.5"
            >¿Por qué elegirme?</a
          >
          <a
            href=""
            class="border-2 rounded-lg border-[#eff3f4] dark:border-[#2c2c2c] text-xs py-2 px-1.5"
            >Colaboremos !</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pt-28">
      <div class="mx-6 flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 font-semibold dark:text-secondary">
              Mi stack
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-terteary max-w-[300px]">
              Creo proyectos funcionales y escalables con estas tecnologías.
            </p>
          </div>

          <button class="text-sm underline">Ver listado completo</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Frontend -->
         <TechFront client:only="react" />
        <!-- Cloud -->
        <TechCloud client:only="react" />
        <!-- Frontend -->
         <TechColaborate client:only="react" />
     
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pt-20 flex flex-col gap-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
        <h2
          class="text-2xl text-gray-800 font-semibold dark:text-secondary mx-6"
        >
          Últimos proyectos
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-6 text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-terteary">
          Explora mis proyectos, donde explico el proceso, la metodología
          utilizada y los detalles clave de su ejecución.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-6 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <main class="flex gap-4">
          <Jobs client:visible />
          <aside class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <div
              class="flex flex-col gap-1 sticky top-[71px] bg-white w-full dark:bg-[#161616]"
            >
              <h3 class="font-semibold">Tech lead - Rand abogados</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-terteary">
                Septiembre 2024, Diciembre 2024
              </p>
            </div>
            <img src="/rand.png" alt="" class="mt-5 rounded-lg" />
            <p class="text-terteary mt-3 line-clamp-5 text-justify">
              ABC Cafe, a local coffee shop with a loyal customer base, wanted
              to undergo a rebranding to attract a younger demographic and stand
              out in a competitive market. The challenge was to modernize their
              brand identity without alienating their existing customers.
            </p>
            <a href="" class="text-terteary">Leer más</a>
          </aside>
        </main>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-6 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <main class="flex gap-4">
          <Jobs client:visible />
          <aside class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <div
              class="flex flex-col gap-1 sticky top-[71px] bg-white w-full dark:bg-[#161616]"
            >
              <h3 class="font-semibold">
                Desarrollador front-end - Medibiologica
              </h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-terteary">
                Septiembre 2024, Diciembre 2024
              </p>
            </div>
            <img src="/rand.png" alt="" class="mt-5 rounded-lg" />
            <p class="text-terteary mt-3">
              ABC Cafe, a local coffee shop with a loyal customer base, wanted
              to undergo a rebranding to attract a younger demographic and stand
